editeur.model.geometry

Interface IShape

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Drawable, Originator, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Composite, Rectangle, Shape, SimplePolygon

    public interface IShape
extends java.lang.Cloneable, Originator, java.io.Serializable, Drawable
    The interface IShape is cloneable and represent the abstraction of a shape. Can be saved and restore with Memento Pattern (Originator). Is Drawable .
